# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PUBLIC, client-safe config. Anything prefixed EXPO_PUBLIC_ is inlined into the
# Expo client bundle by design. This is safe ONLY because Row Level Security
# protects the data (CLAUDE.md §2/§3). Copy this file to .env and fill in.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT-REF.supabase.co
EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key-here

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# SERVER ONLY — NEVER put the service-role key here, never prefix it with
# EXPO_PUBLIC_, never import it from app/ or src/, never commit a real value.
# It lives only in Supabase Edge Function secrets / CI secrets (CLAUDE.md §3, §12).
#   SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=   <-- do NOT set in this file
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# RLS test harness (local / CI only). Points at a PLAIN Postgres, NOT a real
# Supabase project. Locally, `npm run db:local` prints the value to use.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
TEST_DATABASE_URL=postgres://postgres@127.0.0.1:5544/postgres
